                    "effect": "You briefly release the spirits from the  *stormshard* before drawing them back into the glass. Each creature in a 10-foot emanation takes 4d8 void damage (DC 20 basic Fortitude save). You treat the result of your saving throw as one degree of success better than its outcome.",
